Dia. 01 The way of Counting
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par The way of counting-
\par After White plays hane and connects, the changes of the territory have to be checked.
\par It also has to be checked after Black plays hane and connects. The \cf1\b addition and reduction\cf0\b0  of the territory will give the value of this move.
\par
\par After White played hane and connected, White has 8 points and Black has 7 points.
\par
\par }
