Dia. 02 If Black Plays
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black also plays hane and connects with 1 and 3.
\par In this case Black has 8 points and White has 7 points.
\par
\par After counting it shows that the value of the hane and connection (8-7)+(8-7)=\cf1\b 2 points\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
